     <div type="encomium">
   <head>VPON HIS SABBATH.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>WHile <hi>Greenham</hi> writeth of the Sabbaths rest,</l>
      <l>His soule inioyes not which his pen exprest:</l>
      <l>His worke inioyes not what it selfe doth say,</l>
      <l>For it shall neuer finde one resting day.</l>
      <l>A thousand hands shall tosse each page and line,</l>
      <l>Which shall be scanned by a thousand eyne.</l>
      <l>That Sabbaths rest, or this Sabbaths vnrest.</l>
      <l>Hard is to say whether is the happiest.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>I. Hall.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
